#35: FILE: drivers/scsi/dpt_i2o.c:2541:
+			if((rcode = adpt_i2o_reset_hba(pHba)) != 0){

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

